              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "5619 - وَ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "كَتَبَ مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ اَلْحَسَنِ اَلصَّفَّارُ رَضِيَ اَللَّهُ عَنْهُ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " إِلَى "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "أَبِي مُحَمَّدٍ اَلْحَسَنِ بْنِ عَلِيٍّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : رَجُلٌ مَاتَ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " وَ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "تَرَكَ اِبْنَةَ اِبْنَتِهِ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " وَ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "أَخَاهُ لِأَبِيهِ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " وَ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "أُمِّهِ لِمَنْ يَكُونُ اَلْمِيرَاثُ فَوَقَّعَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " فِي"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:4:140:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/139/5169",
        "text": [
          " ذَلِكَ \"اَلْمِيرَاثُ لِلْأَقْرَبِ إِنْ شَاءَ اَللَّهُ\"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.5619 - Muhammad ibn Al-Hasan Al-Saffar (may Allah (swt) be pleased with him) wrote to Abu Muhammad Imam Hasan ibn Ali Al-Askari (as) asking about a man who passed away, leaving behind his daughter's daughter and his full brother.\nImam (as) replied: \"The inheritance belongs to the closest relative, Allah (swt) willing.\""
          ]
        }
      }
